British philosopher Herbert Spencer went a step beyond Darwin's theory of evolution and applied it to the development of human society. In the late 1800s, many Americans enthusiastically embraced Spencer's Social Darwinism to justify laissez-faire, or unrestricted, capitalism.In 1859, Charles Darwin published Origin of Species, which explained his theory of animal and plant evolution based on natural selection..ritish philosopher Herbert Spencer went a step beyond Darwin's theory of evolution and applied it to the development of human society. In the late 1800s, many Americans enthusiastically embraced Spencer's Social Darwinism to justify laissez-faire, or unrestricted, capitalism.
